headline: Hormel Foods Corporation (HRL) Announced 388th Consecutive Quarterly Dividend
summary: On May 19, Hormel Foods Corporation (NYSE:HRL) declared a quarterly dividend of $0.29 per share, which was consistent with its previous dividend. The Minnesota-based multinational food processing company specializes in the production and distribution of branded meat and food products, offering a range of processed meats, poultry items, and prepared foods.
